This example shows how to integrate the custom `Draggable` component within the `DndContext` provider from '@dnd-kit/core'. It demonstrates setting up drag start and drag end handlers to manage the `isDragging` state, which conditionally renders content within a `DragOverlay`. The `Draggable` component wraps a placeholder `Item` component.

```jsx
import React, {useState} from 'react';
