Source: https://docs.dndkit.com/api-documentation/sensors/keyboard

Defines the structure for keyboard codes used to control drag operations. It specifies arrays of keyboard event codes for starting, canceling, and ending a drag.

```typescript
type KeyboardCode = KeyboardEvent['code'];

